ai_summary.summary: The document details the specifications for a 3-phase squirrel cage induction motor required by the Uranium Corporation of India Ltd. at the Tummalapalle Uranium Project. The motor should have a power rating of 7.5 KW (10 HP), specific electrical and mechanical characteristics, and a cast iron body. While the existing make is Kirloskar, all makes are acceptable.
